Text: Looks great, sounds great. Good copy.
Really bad movie. A ridiculous parody. The adventure parody scenes are not funny. Fast forward. What are the meaning of this film? If it is a comedy, it's just not funny.
That attitude is exactly the reason funny assed movies like this never get wide release. People blaming the movie for not being funny when really they just don't get it.
May the glistening chrome of the Borg Queen shed her light upon us all.
